----------------

To compile this code you need the following libraries:

- Boost
- Boost-date-time
- iksemel
- lpthread
- libpqxx

It is recommended iksemel 1.3 due to bug fixes and It's mandatory
for 64bit systems due to compatibility issues.

In order to run the server you need a jabber server
properly configured to accept three components and
the chessd configuration must matchs the jabber config.

Currently only postgresql is supported. So you need to
setup a the postgres server. The database scheme is
located in the database folder.
